nd in turn rediscovers the gifts of life and learning.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAdult college studentsxBiographyxUnited States. 0aAdult college studentszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aCancerxBiographyxPatientsxUnited States. 0aCancerxPatientsvBiographyxUnited States. 0aCancerxPatientszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aCollege presidentsxBiographyxUnited States. 0aCollege presidentszUnited StatesvBiography. 4aeducation. 4alearning. 4ayouth. 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520942073?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520942073423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520942073/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles